                class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-1 text-sm sm:text-base"
              >
                Select up to 5 games you love, and our AI will find your next
                gaming obsession
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-4 space-y-4">
            <div
              class="bg-white/50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 rounded-xl p-4 sm:p-6 backdrop-blur-sm border border-blue-100 dark:border-slate-700"
            >
              <h3
                class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200"
              >
                How it works:
              </h3>
              <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
                <li>
