                  based on your unique gaming DNA
                </li>
                <li>
                  ðŸ“Š <strong>Detailed Insights:</strong> Understanding why each game
                  fits your taste
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <GameSelector
              maxSelection={5}
              buttonText="ðŸ§  Get AI Recommendations"
              id="recommender"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="text-center">
        <div
          class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700"
        >
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
            Powered by Advanced AI
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Our AI assistant leverages deep gaming knowledge and natural
            language processing to understand what makes games special and why
            you might love them. Every recommendation comes with detailed
            reasoning and valuable insights.
          </p>
          <div
            class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
          >
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></span>
              <span>RAWG API Integration</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"></span>
              <span>OpenRouter AI</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full"></span>
              <span>Google Gemini Lite</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-500 rounded-full"></span>
